<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: Buying Pelts, in Halas</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois.cgi?Taklandar">Taklandar</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 9:32 a.m. 21/4/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: Buying Pelts, in Halas<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/forum/mithaniel_marr.cgi?read=45" TARGET=_self>Buying Pelts, in Halas</A> (Kelmar)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>> Hello fellow travellers,

<P>&gt; I am a Shaman by trade and to sustain my
<BR>&gt; family I also hunt animals for
<BR>&gt; their pelt and meat. I tailor the pelts into
<BR>&gt; patchwork armor to sell to
<BR>&gt; the local vendors and adventures alike.
<P>&gt; I am looking for pelts, ruined ones as they
<BR>&gt; are the only ones I can use.
<P>&gt; Ruined Bear Pelts, 1Sp5cp
<BR>&gt; Ruined Cat Pelts, 5SP ( negotiable )
<BR>&gt; Ruined Wolf Pelts, 1Sp
<P>&gt; I also sell PatchWork armor, usually in
<BR>&gt; Large size. However small size
<BR>&gt; is also very available. As for medium size,
<BR>&gt; they would need to be
<BR>&gt; special ordered and more expensive due to
<BR>&gt; the lack of cat pelts , and
<BR>&gt; the danger of hunting snow leopard up here
<BR>&gt; in Halas.
<P>&gt; Large and Small patchworks are 2GP a piece.
<BR>&gt; Medium is 3GP plus 1 cat Pelt or free if 3
<BR>&gt; cat pelts are provided.
<P>&gt; If you find these prices unreasonable please
<BR>&gt; let me know, I would adjust
<BR>&gt; them as appropriate.
<P>&gt; /ooc I am usually on around 9PM EST, give me
<BR>&gt; a tell
<BR>&gt; --
<BR>&gt; Kelvin "Kelmar" Ng
<P>Sounds good to me. I'm from surefall glade and I'll go get some cat pelts for ya if you make me patchwork armor. Medium size.
<P>/ooc I've been having trouble with my comp. lately so it might be a few days untill I can get online.
<P>Maybe we could go hunt cats together on the karanas plains. BTW I'm a half-elf ranger, made to hunt!!
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
